# Aero Compiler & Runtime

Shared **parsing and codegen** live in **`packages/compiler`** (`@aero-js/compiler`). **Vite integration, Aero-specific codegen, and runtime** live in **`packages/core`** (`@aero-js/core`).

## Modules (`packages/compiler/src`)

- **parser.ts** — Extract script blocks from HTML; use constants from **constants.ts** (`ATTR_IS_BUILD`, `ATTR_IS_INLINE`, `COMPONENT_SUFFIX_REGEX`, `ATTR_FOR`, etc.)
- **build-script-analysis.ts** — AST-based analysis of build script content (oxc-parser): imports and `export function getStaticPaths`; used by codegen.
- **tokenizer.ts** — Re-exports from `@aero-js/interpolation` for text/attribute compilation.
- **codegen.ts**, **lowerer/**, **emit.ts** — Template → render function pipeline.
- **resolver.ts** — Resolve component/layout paths against path aliases (from project tsconfig).
- **helpers.ts** — Interpolation helpers (`compileInterpolation`, `compileAttributeInterpolation`).

## Modules (`packages/core/src`)

- **codegen/** — Aero-specific codegen (client scripts, blocking scripts, Vite hooks) layered on the compiler.
- **vite/** — Vite plugin: virtual modules for client scripts; use `\0` prefix for Vite virtual module IDs (not `/@aero/client/` in emitted IDs).
- **vite/build.ts** — Build orchestration, page discovery, Nitro integration.
- **runtime/** — `Aero` class, instance context, client entry (`client.ts`, `index.ts`, `instance.ts`).
- **utils/** — `aliases.ts`, `routing.ts`, etc.

## Constants (`packages/compiler/src/constants.ts`)

Use named constants: `ATTR_PROPS`, `ATTR_FOR`, `ATTR_IF`, `ATTR_ELSE_IF`, `ATTR_ELSE`, `ATTR_IS_BUILD`, `ATTR_IS_INLINE`, `ATTR_IS_BLOCKING`, `TAG_SLOT`, `SLOT_NAME_DEFAULT`, `COMPONENT_SUFFIX_REGEX`, `CURLY_INTERPOLATION_REGEX`, `ALPINE_ATTR_REGEX`, `VOID_TAGS`.

## TDD (red-to-green)

When implementing new features or tracking down bugs, use TDD: (1) write or run a failing test that captures the behavior or reproduces the bug (red); (2) implement the minimal change to make the test pass (green); (3) refactor if needed. For bugs, always add or adjust a failing test first; do not skip to the fix.

## Tests

- **packages/compiler** — `src/__tests__/` (parser, codegen, build-script-analysis, etc.).
- **packages/core** — `src/**/__tests__/` (vite, codegen, runtime).
- Run from repo root: `pnpm test`.

